data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of comfort and space in this fantastic 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located in Killeen. Boasting a generous 3,126 square feet, this residence offers ample room to live and grow. Step inside and appreciate the open floor plan that seamlessly connects the various living spaces. The formal dining room adds an elegant touch, making gatherings and entertaining a delight. One of the highlights of this home is the master bedroom conveniently situated downstairs, providing a private oasis to retreat to. The spacious bedrooms offer versatile options for your family's needs. 

Outside, the fenced backyard beckons with possibilities, ready for your personal touch. Imagine creating cherished memories in this outdoor space, perfect for relaxation and play. Enjoy the convenience of this location—close to the middle school, YMCA, and just 1.5 miles from a park. Additionally, shopping is a breeze, with a mere 5-10 minutes drive to local retail destinations.

This well-designed property offers the comfort and convenience you've been searching for. Don't miss the chance to call this your new home. Schedule a showing today! Additional Note: The sale is 'AS-IS,' and the seller will not be making any repairs.
